Events.RelatedDescription: Opened pull request "Bump gittools/actions from 2 to 3" (#1824) at dotnet/Open-XML-SDK
Events.RelatedBody:
Bumps [gittools/actions](https://github.com/gittools/actions) from 2 to 3.
Release notes

Sourced from gittools/actions's releases.

v3.0.0

What's Changed

  • #1193 - Drop GitVersion legacy output variables by @​arturcic in GitTools/actions#1195

  • #1193 - Drop GitVersion legacy output variables by @​arturcic in GitTools/actions#1201

  • Add markdown linting by @​arturcic in GitTools/actions#1202

  • Improve testability by @​arturcic in GitTools/actions#1204

  • Add gitversion/command task/action, remove additionalArguments from gitversion/execute by @​arturcic in GitTools/actions#1203

  • Bump eslint-config-love from 56.0.0 to 57.0.0 by @​dependabot in GitTools/actions#1190

  • Bump @​typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin from 7.16.1 to 7.17.0 by @​dependabot in GitTools/actions#1191

  • Bump typescript from 5.5.3 to 5.5.4 by @​dependabot in GitTools/actions#1189

  • Bump the vite group with 2 updates by @​dependabot in GitTools/actions#1194

  • (npm): Bump @​types/node from 20.14.11 to 20.14.12 by @​dependabot in GitTools/actions#1198

  • (npm): Bump the eslint group with 2 updates by @​dependabot in GitTools/actions#1197

  • Bump eslint-plugin-vitest from 0.4.1 to 0.5.4 by @​dependabot in GitTools/actions#1173

Full Changelog: https://github.com/GitTools/actions/compare/v2.0.1...v3.0.0

v2.0.1

What's Changed

  • #1184 - allow GRM versions up to 0.20.0 by @​arturcic in GitTools/actions#1185
  • #1183 - updated examples to use the correct GRM arguments by @​arturcic in GitTools/actions#1186

Full Changelog: https://github.com/GitTools/actions/compare/v2.0.0...v2.0.1

v0.10.2 - fix for v0.10.0 and v0.10.1

No release notes provided.

Commits
  • 0ad7bfb include stdout and stderr in the output of the tools
  • 1b0ab26 dist update
  • 000e20d Merge pull request #1341 from arturcic/fix/include-sdtout-stderr
  • 5788f8a include stdout and stderr in the output of the tools
  • 771005a update envs
  • 1a8f9bd use macos-15 for GHA
  • 72eb276 update examples version to 3.0.1
  • 95890b4 Merge pull request #1337 from GitTools/dependabot/npm_and_yarn/vite-925092cb23
  • 5e1eabf (npm): Bump the vite group with 2 updates
  • 37fbfed Merge pull request #1335 from GitTools/dependabot/npm_and_yarn/eslint-30cfb28c55
  • Additional commits viewable in compare view
